<dialogue boes="2.0.0">
    <personality id="200">
        <title>Dying Man</title>
        <look>
            <![CDATA[This is a withered, dying man, sitting and shivering on a filthy pallet. He looks like he's been heavily worked over by Jaen's men, and left here to die. It's a pitiful sight.]]>
        </look>
        <name>
            <![CDATA[He looks up but doesn't seem to see you. "I am ... I am ... I forget."]]>
        </name>
        <job>
            <![CDATA["I was a shopkeeper," he croaks. "I don't have much time left."]]>
        </job>
        <unknown>
            <![CDATA[He chokes.]]>
        </unknown>
    </personality>
    <personality id="201">
        <title>Marv</title>
        <look>
            <![CDATA[You find a man waiting for you by a hole in the ground.]]>
        </look>
        <name>
            <![CDATA["Real name isn't important. If you get caught, they'll get it out of you anyway. Just call me Marv."]]>
        </name>
        <job>
            <![CDATA["I was sent here by Stalker. I'm going to give you instructions now."]]>
        </job>
        <unknown>
            <![CDATA["We don't have time for this."]]>
        </unknown>
    </personality>
